Logs/

## JetBrains Rider / IntelliJ
.idea/
*.sln.DotSettings.user

## Visual Studio Code
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace
.history/

## Mono / Xamarin / Mac
*.userprefs
mono_crash.*

## NuGet Packages
*.nupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/repositories.config
project.lock.json
project.assets.json

## Node.js / Front-end Tooling (Tailwind CSS, npm)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.npm/
.yarn/
.pnpm-store/

## Local Environment / User Settings
*.env
*.env.local
*.env.*.local
appsettings.json
appsettings.local.json
appsettings.Development.json

## Custom project files & AI tool caches
.gemini/
.antigravitycli/

## Operating System files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db


